# Author: Duy BG VN
# ZETA AI - Database Backup Storage

# This directory stores database backups and snapshots
# Critical for disaster recovery and data protection

# Structure:
# database/
# ├── daily/           # Daily automated backups
# ├── weekly/          # Weekly full backups
# ├── monthly/         # Monthly archive backups
# ├── snapshots/       # Point-in-time snapshots
# └── migrations/      # Database migration backups

# Backup Schedule:
# - Daily incremental: 02:00 UTC
# - Weekly full: Sunday 01:00 UTC
# - Monthly archive: 1st day 00:00 UTC
# - Pre-migration snapshots: Before each migration

# Retention Policy:
# - Daily backups: 7 days
# - Weekly backups: 4 weeks
# - Monthly backups: 12 months
# - Snapshots: 48 hours

# Security:
# - All backups are encrypted at rest
# - Access logs are maintained
# - Integrity checks performed daily

# Keep this directory in git but exclude actual backup files
